---
title: Faster-Than-Takeout Turkey Wonton Soup with Bok Choy, Cabbage, Carrots & Wonton Strips
description: Enjoy the savory flavors of homemade wonton soup with our quick and clever shortcut! This "deconstructed" version stars savory ground pork simmered in a umami-rich broth. Tender wonton wrappers cook in a flash along with bok choy and cabbage. Serve with a shower of scallion greens and crunchy wonton strips for a meal that's even better than take-out!
